RRULE:FREQ=DAILY
END:VEVENT

BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:systems-update-monthly@ifala-openclaw
DTSTAMP:20260413T211000Z
SUMMARY:systems update monthly reminder
DESCRIPTION:Reminder mensile per aggiornare SYSTEMS.md.
